        <num>45-3-13</num>
        <content>
          <p>The oath prescribed in Code Section 45-3-11 shall be in the following form:</p>
          <p>"I, ________________________ (Name) a citizen of ______________ and being an employee of ________________________ and the recipient of public funds for services rendered as such employee, do hereby solemnly swear and affirm that I will support the Constitution of the United States and the Constitution of Georgia."</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1949, p. 960, ยง 3; Ga. L. 1950, p. 282, ยง 1; Ga. L. 2015, p. 385, ยง 5-4/HB 252.)</p>
          <p>The 2015 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2015, deleted "and that I am not a member of the Communist Party" following "the Constitution of Georgia" at the end of this Code section.</p>
        </content>
